{"tid":1474641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國前領導人語錄 預視中國對香港問題處理手法","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T17:11:39.000Z","uid":68125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3cb96851a597289fcb0e5f0e5a761f02fbe62e","tid":1474641,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:56:17.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1083973875138846?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1083973875138846%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=89b1bf15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1083973875138846?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n中國民航局對國泰施壓<br />\n咁港航見到大台咁既處境，仲唔即刻做野咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國覺得一國兩制舉世成功，係因為係可以喺原有制度下，香港代理者實行中國政策。即係話，而家香港處境，中國方面周恩來早喺50年代講左：「任何（令香港）邁向自治領土狀況的舉措，將都會被視作非常不友善。」<br />\n簡單咁講，雙普選喺中國眼中係同香港獨立無異<br />\n<br />\n香港下場係點，中國時任總理趙紫陽既說話可以預見到，佢講左：「如在「主權」和「香港的繁榮穩定」兩個原則之間抉擇，中國政府會將主權放在繁榮穩定之上。」</span></span><br />\n明既就明"},{"pid":"bbe486c6279c99cd5a03c7847fb137b19216c26d","tid":1474641,"uid":92467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:57:19.000Z","msg":"14年已經知"},{"pid":"e2c3f417d9e44222a2aa27a759f38ded165cb282","tid":1474641,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"而家係睇主權+管治威信同黨員資產"},{"pid":"cf8c7b80b33edcad2e72b47fc83931e3297756a0","tid":1474641,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3cb96851a597289fcb0e5f0e5a761f02fbe62e","tid":1474641,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:56:17.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1083973875138846?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.co